description.en: CliffsNotes study guides are written by real teachers and professors, so no matter what you're studying, CliffsNotes can ease your homework headaches and help you score high on exams.
description.ga_IE: Scríobhadh treoracha staidéir Cliffsnotes ag fíor-mhúinteoirí agus Ollúna, mar sin is cuma cad atá tú ag staidéar, is féidir le CliffsNotes do chuireann obair bhaile a mhaolú agus cabhrú leat scór ard ar scrúduithe.
